== Project Working Group ==

 * project leader is [[LarsNoschinskiEn| Lars Noschinski]]
 * Urgent Call is on http://swpat.ffii.org/xatra/cons0406
 * subscribe to [[http://lists.ffii.org/mailman/listinfo/consilium-parl/|consilium-parl mailing list]]
 * government addresses http://www.europa.eu.int/abc/governments/index_en.htm

The following wiki pages are used for this project:

 * LtrCons0406En - this page, general informations
 * LtrConsRecv0406En - organise the organisation of national deliveries
 * !LtrConsRecv<Country>0406<Language> - national delivery organisation page, provides list of recipients, maybe national delivery instructions for users
 * LtrConsSend0406En - general and easy instructions, how to send the letter, links national "Send" pages
 * !LtrConsSend<Country>0406<Language> - national pages where people should note, to whom they sent a letter, see e.g. LtrConsSendFr0406Fr and overview at LtrConsSend0406En

== Tasks (ordered by priority) ==

 * Find the Recipients in the National Governments/Political Parties: LtrConsRecv0406En
 * Translations / Typesetting
 * Signature Collection
 * Sending: LtrConsSend0406En

