=== Typesetting the text with logos nicely  ===

==== Existing Samples ====

These samples have no reference to the appendixes, you also need to change/remove the date and add either a personal cover letter or just "Dear <Recipient>, ..."

 * http://swpat.ffii.org/letters/cons0406/LtrConsMinim0406.en.pdf
 * http://swpat.ffii.org/letters/cons0406/LtrConsMinim0406.en.sxw
 * http://swpat.ffii.org/letters/cons0406/LtrConsMinim0406.de.pdf
 * http://swpat.ffii.org/letters/cons0406/LtrConsMinim0406.de.sxw
 * http://swpat.ffii.org/letters/cons0406/LtrConsMinim0406.fr.pdf
 * http://swpat.ffii.org/letters/cons0406/LtrConsMinim0406.fr.sxw

 * Not every signator needs to be represented on paper with a logo.  No need for masses of penguins. 

 * The [[http://swpat.ffii.org/papers/eubsa-swpat0202/ipat0304/ipat0304.pdf|Joint Patent Industry Statement of 2003-04]] might serve as a model or as something to parody.
 * find company logos at genba.ffii.org in ''var/www/img/logos'' or collect them here after picking them from the company's website

== Appendices ==

 * separate document and each appendix separately: allow people to send with additional appendices
 * complete the appendices 
   * [[ConsText0406En| A]] (pdf: [[http://swpat.ffii.org/xatra/cons0406/text/ConsText0406.cs.pdf|cs]], [[http://swpat.ffii.org/xatra/cons0406/text/ConsText0406.de.pdf|de]], [[http://swpat.ffii.org/xatra/cons0406/text/ConsText0406.en.pdf|en]], [[http://swpat.ffii.org/xatra/cons0406/text/ConsText0406.fr.pdf|fr]]) completed by phm, see static version, nearly perfect
