== Translation ==

 * translate [[http://swpat.ffii.org/letters/cons0406/LtrCons0406.en.txl|source text]] according to [[http://swpat.ffii.org/group/langtxt/|instructions]], but send to mail processor mlhtimport at a2e de (mlhtimport at ffii org doesn't work reliably at the moment).

In addition also create the sxw/pdf files (or files using other text processing systems at which you are good, resulting in PDF). See "Typesetting the Text with logos nicely" above.

== Signature Collection ==

 * collect signatures of big players and politicians (e.g. those from Calls for Action [[http://swpat.ffii.org/papri/eubsa-swpat0202/cpedu/|1]] & [[http://swpat.ffii.org/papri/europarl0309/cpedu/|2]]) and submit to cpedu-help at ffii org
   * Did a [[http://ffii.org/~schinski/mail-draft.mbox|not-good-enough draft]] for a mail to german companies who signed !CfA I/II, but will not be able to incorporate changes till Sun, 2004-06-20. Told jmaebe about it, he might want to do an english version. ccorn already prepared a list of recipients. (schinski)

